{"word":"ἔκλυτος","slug":"ἔκλυτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἔκλυτος</b></el> <el>(ἔκλῠτος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐκλύω'><el>ἐκλύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>easy to let go, light, buoyant</i>, of missiles, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>ἐκλύτως</el>, <i>remissly</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}